quran[6{c,v,t}:
2,197,"hajj ke mahinay sab ko maloom hain jo shakhs un muqarrar mahino mein hajj ki niyat kere, ussay khabardaar rehna chahiye ke hajj ke douran is se koi shehwani feal, koi bad amli, koi larai jhagrre ki baat sarzad nah ho aur jo naik kaam tum karo ge, woh Allah ke ilm mein hoga safar hajj ke liye zaad raah sath le jao, aur sab se behtar zaad raah parhaiz gari hai pas ae hosh mndo! Meer y na farmani se parhaiz karo"
2,198,"aur agar hajj ke sath sath apne Rab ka fazl bhi talaash karte jao, to is mein koi muzaiqa nahi phir jab Arfat se chalo, to Musher haraam ( mzdlfh ) ke paas theharkar Allah ko yaad karo aur uss terhan yaad karo, jis ki hadaayat is ne tumhe di hai, warna is se pehlay tum log bhatkay hue thay"
2,199,"phir jahan se sab log palatne hain wahein se tum bhi paltoo aur Allah se maffi chaho, yaqeenan woh maaf karne wala aur reham frmane wala hai"
2,200,"phir jab apne hajj ke arkaan ada kar chicco, to jis terhan pehlay apne aaba o ajdaad ka zikar karte thay, uss terhan ab Allah ka zikar karo, balkay is se bhi barh kar ( magar Allah ko yaad karne walay logon mein bhi bohat farq hai ) unn mein se koi to aisa hai, jo kehta hai ke ae hamaray Rab, hamein duniya hi mein sab kuch deeday aisay shakhs ke liye akhirat mein koi hissa nahi"
2,201,aur koi kehta hai ke ae hamaray Rab! hamein duniya mein bhi bhalai day aur akhirat mein bhi bhalai aur aag ke azaab se hamein bacha
2,202,aisay log apni kamaai ke mutabiq ( dono jagah ) hissa payen ge aur Allah ko hisaab chkate kuch der nahi lagti
